{"tid":703110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【齊鼓掌】揸綿羊仔自炒遭旅巴輾腳，32歲女警重創命危","createTime":"2018-06-15T12:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T07:45:15.000Z","uid":29314,"like":56,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d0acfdda1b4b29ad3a295f1c34c842286e8523b3","tid":703110,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"青衣今早發生嚴重車禍，今早6時許，一名32歲姓葉女警駕駛電單車回警署上班途中，駛經青敬路海悅花園對開時懷疑失控自炒，她受傷倒卧地上，尾隨旅遊巴收掣不及輾過其雙腳，其他駕駛人士見狀報案。她事後由救護車送往瑪嘉烈醫院搶救，情況危殆。警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n共業！"},{"pid":"1525fb88f7b4c742e4371b5984532bdf36d46111","tid":703110,"uid":171107,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:50:01.000Z","msg":"女人揸車加黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ad9daecf3870545f4b68ecd64483c6b51ec963","tid":703110,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c2800f34a606b58b88f3b3feb1f923c195c88b","tid":703110,"uid":188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:52:08.000Z","msg":"好在係上班途中 如果唔係比佢拎到工傷"},{"pid":"3a16dd60ffe905171361f6457e317d3dbf0b4cac","tid":703110,"uid":29314,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:53:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好在係上班途中 如果唔係比佢拎到工傷</blockquote><br />\n你放心。<br />\n<br />\n黑警實夾錢捐畀佢。"},{"pid":"a387bbbf3c3a47d7cc7724b197f29843bb61fdca","tid":703110,"uid":44783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a16dd60ffe905171361f6457e317d3dbf0b4cac","tid":703110,"uid":29314,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:53:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好在係上班途中 如果唔係比佢拎到工傷</bl